### Get all expenses
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses

### Get expense by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/1

### Create new expense - Lunch
POST http://localhost:8080/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Lunch",
  "amount": 12.50,
  "category": "Food",
  "date": "2024-12-19"
}

